Located in the Santa Catarina Street - Oporto’s most famous shopping street - the Studios Porto Solar are cosy and ideal for those who want to visit the historical centre of the city.

With all the commerce (clothing, shoes, jewellery, bakery and traditional pastries, supermarkets, bookshops, etc) at a 5-minute walk and the public transportations necessary from/for the airport and other cities of Portugal as well as for the beaches and touristic attractions.

With 40m2, they are simply decorated and elevator accessible. They include cable TV, Wi-Fi and are ideal for an independent stay, offering all the necessary utensils to prepare meals.

In addition to the central location and the kindness and friendliness of our staff, we're pleased to provide you the following services:
•Touristic informations;
•Car, scooter and bike rental;
•Souvenirs;
•Ticket office for Tours, cruises and hop-on hop-off bus;
•Garage place for an extra fee of 10€/day that needs to be reserved in advance;
• Airport transfer with an additional fee;

The reception is open every day from 8h30 until 19h. You can ask for any additional information at the reception, by phone or email.

